      <title>壳牌将 SouthCoast Wind Energy 股份出售给 Ocean Winds North America</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/shell-sells-stake-southcoast-wind-energy-ocean-winds-north-america-2024-03-20/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[能源公司壳牌周三表示，已将其持有的 SouthCoast Wind Energy 50% 的股份出售给其合资伙伴 Ocean Winds North America，该公司的成立目的是开发马萨诸塞州沿海的风电项目，具体金额未公开。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/shell-sells-stake-southcoast-wind-energy-ocean-winds-north-america-2024-03-20/</guid>
